title: MacOS X 10.4.8 Tiger VMWare image by Evil Chemist
description:
This torrent contains a 7-zipped VMWare image for MacOX 10.4.8 (created from JaS AMD-Intel-SSE2-SSE3 with PPF1 & PPF2 image). VMWare Workstation ACE Edition 6.0.2 build-59824 was used for image creation.
Use 7zip (http://www.7zip.org) to unpack and enjoy the best OS ever.

P.S. WinRAR gave me a 1.8G file on maximum compression, while 7-zip produced less than a 1.4G file (22% less!). Save ya time, go open source!
